1333
01:07:46.128 --> 01:07:50.099
Like is he crazy? Should
I be worried about him?

1334
01:07:50.132 --> 01:07:52.134
Well. this kid has had
several psych evaluations

1335
01:07:52.168 --> 01:07:54.070
