trying to do here right now.

1392
01:10:56.485 --> 01:10:57.987
what's right.

1393
01:11:02.258 --> 01:11:06.695
Okay. Tell me. What did you find out?

1394
01:11:06.729 --> 01:11:11.767
Well. first off. I think Dylan killed Ryan

1395
